#### 5.1.5. Transform Types

| Transform Type | Description | Example |
|---------------|-------------|---------|
| `field_mappings` | Rename fields | `"max_tokens"` → `"maxOutputTokens"` |
| `extract_system_message` | Move system message to top-level | For Anthropic API |
| `role_mapping` | Rename role values | `"assistant"` → `"model"` |
| `wrap` | Wrap body in container | Add metadata fields |
| `flatten` | Flatten nested structures | `generationConfig.temp` → `temperature` |
| `remove_fields` | Remove fields from body | Strip `model` for Azure |
| `defaults` | Inject default values | Set default `temperature` |
| `template` | Apply JSONPath template | Complex restructuring |

