### 5.2. The Backend Resource

**Endpoint:** `POST /v1/backends`
**Purpose:** Groups Providers and applies orchestration policies (load balancing, resilience, health checks).

```json
{
  "id": "backend_hybrid_prod",
  "name": "Hybrid Production Cluster",
  "spec": {
    "load_balancing": {
      "algorithm": "failover",
      "sticky_sessions": false
    },

    "providers": [
      { 
        "ref": "provider_openai_prod", 
        "priority": 1, 
        "weight": 100 
      },
      { 
        "ref": "provider_azure_fallback", 
        "priority": 2, 
        "weight": 0 
      }
    ],

    "timeout": {
      "connect": "2s",
      "response": "600s",
      "idle": "60s"
    },

    "retry": {
      "attempts": 3,
      "backoff": {
        "initial": "100ms",
        "max": "10s",
        "multiplier": 2
      },
      "conditions": ["5xx", "connect-failure", "reset"]
    },

    "circuit_breaker": {
      "enabled": true,
      "error_threshold_percentage": 50,
      "min_request_volume": 20,
      "sleep_window": "30s",
      "half_open_requests": 5
    },

    "health_check": {
      "type": "active",
      "interval": "10s",
      "timeout": "5s",
      "path": "/health",
      "healthy_threshold": 2,
      "unhealthy_threshold": 3,
      "expected_statuses": [200, 204]
    }
  }
}
```

**Supported Load Balancing Algorithms:**

| Algorithm | Behavior | Use Case |
|-----------|----------|----------|
| `failover` | Uses highest priority provider; falls back on failure | Primary/backup setups |
| `round_robin` | Distributes evenly across healthy providers | Even load distribution |
| `weighted` | Distributes based on weight values | Gradual rollouts, A/B testing |
| `least_connections` | Routes to provider with fewest active connections | Variable latency providers |

### 5.3. The Route Resource

**Endpoint:** `POST /v1/routes`
**Purpose:** Defines the entry point, matching logic, and policy filters.

```json
{
  "id": "route_chat_v1",
  "host": "org-1.gateway.com",
  "spec": {
    "match": {
      "path": "/v1/chat",
      "type": "prefix",
      "methods": ["POST"]
    },

    "filters": [
      { 
        "name": "auth_jwt", 
        "config": { "issuer": "clerk" },
        "on_error": "terminate"
      },
      { 
        "name": "pii_masking", 
        "config": { "types": ["ssn", "email", "credit_card"] },
        "on_error": "log_and_continue"
      },
      { 
        "name": "rate_limit", 
        "config": { 
          "limits": [
            { "limit": 100, "window": "1m", "key": "request", "scope": "api_key" },
            { "limit": 50000, "window": "1m", "key": "token", "scope": "api_key" }
          ]
        },
        "on_error": "terminate"
      }
    ],

    "backend_ref": "backend_hybrid_prod"
  }
}
```

