| Filter | Description | Config Example |
|--------|-------------|----------------|
| `rate_limit` | Multi-dimensional rate limiting | See below |
| `concurrent_limit` | Limit concurrent requests | `{ "max": 10, "scope": "api_key" }` |
| `quota` | Usage quotas (daily/monthly) | `{ "limit": 1000000, "period": "month", "key": "token" }` |

