**Rate Limiting Algorithms:**

| Algorithm | Description | Use Case |
|-----------|-------------|----------|
| `fixed_window` | Reset counter at window boundary | Simple, predictable |
| `sliding_window` | Rolling window calculation | Smoother limiting |
| `token_bucket` | Tokens refill over time, allows bursts | Best for APIs |
| `leaky_bucket` | Constant drain rate | Smooth traffic shaping |

**Rate Limit Keys:**

| Key | Description | Extracted From |
|-----|-------------|----------------|
| `request` | Count requests | N/A |
| `token` | Count tokens | Request body or response |
| `byte` | Count bytes | Request/response size |
| `cost` | Estimated cost | Model + tokens |

**Rate Limit Scopes:**

| Scope | Description | Identifier Source |
|-------|-------------|-------------------|
| `global` | Across all requests | N/A |
| `tenant` | Per tenant | Subdomain or JWT claim |
| `api_key` | Per API key | Auth filter metadata |
| `user` | Per user | JWT `sub` claim |
| `ip` | Per IP address | `X-Forwarded-For` or connection |
| `route` | Per route | Route ID |
| `custom` | Custom expression | JSONPath expression |

