## 8. Conflict Resolution Strategy

| Conflict Type | Strategy | Implementation |
| --- | --- | --- |
| **User vs. User** | **Strict Isolation** | Users are assigned unique subdomains (`tenant.gateway.com`). No cross-tenant routing possible. |
| **Route vs. Route** | **Longest Prefix Match** | If a user defines `/api` and `/api/v1`, the Radix Trie automatically routes `/api/v1` to the more specific rule. |
| **Filter Order** | **Phase + Definition Order** | Global filters run before route filters within each phase. Within same phase, order follows config array. |
| **Config Version** | **Last Write Wins** | Controller maintains version numbers; gateways reject stale updates. |

